Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙 凜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地來接我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們兩個都辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於習慣這個泳池了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後天正式比賽的時候觀眾席就都會坐滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊張嗎 小憐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我們可是為了這壹天壹直在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是緊張的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心臟終於強大了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴前輩他們快回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經這個時候了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小憐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙前輩 會開開心心地回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 壹定會打起精神回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都從今天開始進賽場遊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向著比賽挑戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和我的隊伍匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:52.96,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,500)\pos(934,624)}13Fr 初始的永恒之夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸 憐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能平安回來太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小憐可擔心妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉讓妳們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 為了後天的比賽要好好休息身體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就是向著正式比賽的最終挑戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴 諸 憐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想跟妳們說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今為止都不執著於速度和勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因為想遊而遊泳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是執著於速度勝負的話 我遊泳就沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這麽想的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜有向世界前進的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了這個夢想而投身於競泳的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽我 要因為想要遊泳的夢想而進入競泳的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進入勝負的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和凜不壹樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有他那樣堅定的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 妳們問我的時候我也沒法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為就算去尋找夢想也不壹定找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是被凜帶著 看了各種景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了世界的寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果找到了 怎麽辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在那個世界遊泳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想繼續遊泳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我會執著於速度和勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了自己的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然這次旅行對遙來說是特殊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這就是遙前輩找到的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會全力支持妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 凜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的時候有發生什麽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家狀態都很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜前輩 求禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.49,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,真煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考拉 袋鼠 考拉 袋鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.66,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,是回旋鏢啊 看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.04,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,真是再適合妳不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.92,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,yes！yes！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似會晚壹點來匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是全國大賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…之前對妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前程的事 壹直沒有說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得自己不適合競泳的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負的世界不適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以會呆呆地想要不要去本地的大學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有什麽別的想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這期間 幫笹部教練的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壹開始只覺得是幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但後來覺得教小孩子們遊泳很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和颯鬥相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想教他遊泳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙還給猶豫的我提出建議了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颯鬥終於能遊仰泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說他不害怕了 很好玩的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想讓更多的孩子知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊泳的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成為教遊泳的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了學習這個而去東京的大學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我找到的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳壹定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是接下來學習就痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回位太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要註意重心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山崎前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 凜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那麽亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 亂來也有回報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是比賽前夜 就不要客氣隨便點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這頓老師請客
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 老師土豪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽就要土豆沙拉 海鮮沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸魚薯條 烤牛肉 洋蔥湯 約克布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛤蜊意面 辣味番茄意面 漁夫意面 鰻魚凍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辣味炸土豆 芝士蛋卷 芝士焗飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上龍蝦黃金燒 烤龍蝦 龍蝦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉月君 先點這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 龍蝦什麽的還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸君妳也太不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青花魚味增湯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽會有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不過有炸青花魚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有鹽烤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.72,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麽總是青花魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.09,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,我們趕緊下單吧 下單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.10,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,您好點單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.26,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 諸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七瀨君給人的感覺變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明前壹陣 感覺他們之間氣氛有點緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.56,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,有鹽燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.56,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,遙別再糾結這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像和哥哥壹起去澳大利亞後 找到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.39,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.19,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.48,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,魚肉濃湯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.61,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,嘗嘗看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.15,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有日本菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.40,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,日本菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.32,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙想吃日本菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飽了 吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是吃的有點多了啊 諸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 因為我正在成長期嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我們可是要出場全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要繃緊精神才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海面閃閃發光的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和巖鳶的海完全不壹樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是明天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從創建遊泳部開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們竟然能走到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的時候 連泳池都沒法用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯 是從修理泳池開始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候的小遙 壹心只想著遊泳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 在去家居店的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在泳衣前面突然就開始脫衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是無法置信…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 那時候憐還沒有入部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是田徑部的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 最初真的是完全意義不明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 被諸君邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又看了遙前輩的泳姿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 卻跟不上大家的步調
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在合宿的時候還被真琴前輩所救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有大家在 我才
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了遊泳的…接力的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才走到了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壹切都多虧了 諸說出想創建遊泳部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就不要再提了 小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸妳真的很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 離家出走真是嚇壞了我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 之後真的很努力的讓社團與學習兩不耽誤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我 憐才厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從旱鴨子到學會蝶泳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算護目鏡歪了也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個壹點都不美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有那種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的憐 現在已經可以遊全種類了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有 這都是多虧了凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯 都虧是凜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麽會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 因為憐好像在拼命隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知 知道了就說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很感謝凜學長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很感謝凜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他再會 然後競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擦身而過 失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但正因為這些 我才註意到了大家的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得想和大家壹起遊接力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候的接力 是我們4個人第壹次的接力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的時候 只想著壹定要好好交接給下壹個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後做了好多好多的練習 參加了各種比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家壹起的遊接力變得非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是輸給鮫柄的時候 真的很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 多虧了凜壹直在督促著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 我們就開始猛練習交接來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地方大賽上拿出來結果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 明年我們也許能去更厲害的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做許多許多練習 去好多好多次合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家壹起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說什麽呢 諸君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年級生明天大賽結束後 就隱退了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是每天的練習 還是合宿 比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有接力…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們四個在明年已經不可能實現的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小憐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 我…還想繼續遊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小遙 和小真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有小憐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四人就壹直這樣遊下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明終於 終於
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學會遊泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然就這樣結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭了 諸 憐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 沒什麽可哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我們四人要壹起遊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽都沒有結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們被接力連結著 壹路到達了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 就算我們前進的方向不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後我們也壹定是 相互連結著的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不存在所謂的結束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能再次看到那從未看到過的景色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠我們四人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男子400米接力 第壹組的比賽馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴學長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小憐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了 沒人能贏我嗎 百
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饒了我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們三年級就隱退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了四月會有新的部員加入 組成新的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望這會成為最棒的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這之後又有新的隊伍誕生 繼承我們的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們就朝著這永遠的夢想壹直前進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天還是沒哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下壹任部長是妳 拜托妳了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.91,Default top,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教哦 似鳥部長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點傷算什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隨意放棄自己的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會壹直等下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等妳回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 妳的話壹定會這麽說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊 我會考慮下的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥不回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不明白嗎 蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥要好好學習天天向上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 壹定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 已經這個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒轍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 航班要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了不要加「小」了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸 憐 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 去小凜那邊前有個要去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫著我們在那場接力賽看到的沒有見過的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去好有趣啊 讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦 笹部教練
